library(titanic)
d=titanic_train
male = d %>% filter(Sex=='male')
female = d %>% filter(Sex=='female')
d$surv=factor(d$Survived)
d$sex=factor(d$Sex)
ggplot(d, aes( x=Sex, y=Age, color=factor(Survived) ) )+ geom_jitter()
